data.description: Welcome home to this charming brick rancher nestled in a cul-de-sac of the sought after Salem Lakes neighborhood! With three  bedrooms, two baths, and an inviting open floor plan, it's the perfect blend of comfort and style. Fall in love with the modern touches of this  updated kitchen and baths, complete with tile flooring for easy maintenance. Enjoy cozy evenings by the wood-burning stove inserted in the  den or entertain guests in the spacious living area. Say goodbye to weekend chores with the low-maintenance yard, allowing you to spend  more time relaxing and enjoying the beautiful surroundings. Don't miss out on this gem! Schedule your showing today and prepare to be  impressed!
